data.description: Welcome to this adorable 3 bed, 2 bath home with beautiful mountain views and easy access to get to town. This home has recently had all carpets replaced, got a fresh coat of paint, has all new blinds with privacy and black out screens, as well as new lighting fixtures throughout. You will find a spacious living room and a large kitchen with pantry, new appliances, and lots of natural light. The large master bedroom offers a slider to the back patio, walk-in closet, dual sinks with lots of counter space, and a walk-in shower. The home also offers two spacious guest bedrooms, indoor laundry, and a new house filtration system. You will love drinking your morning coffee under the covered patio while enjoying the beautiful mountain views. The backyard has so much potential with tons of space, so bring all your ideas!
